        public LogLevel MinLogLevel { get => _minLogLevel ; set => _minLogLevel = value ; }

        public bool ? IsEnabledDebuggerTarget { get => _isEnabledDebuggerTarget ; set => _isEnabledDebuggerTarget = value ; }

